rows.label: qst201412_msg0003
rows.name:
But this is exactly the sort of time
when you need to be able to perk
yourself up!

rows.label: qst201412_msg0004
rows.name:
Well, there's no one here. Why don't
we talk about fashion or something to
pass the time?

rows.label: qst201412_msg0005
rows.name:
Sure, why not. How about accessories?
I love accessories!

rows.label: qst201412_msg0006
rows.name:
I mean, I like wearing them, of course.
But just looking at them's fun too!

rows.label: qst201412_msg0007
rows.name: What kind of things do you like, Zakuro?

rows.label: qst201412_msg0009
rows.name: Hmmm... I guess I'm really into flowers.

rows.label: qst201412_msg0010
rows.name:
Flowers are so pretty, cute and stylish.
I feel kinda healed whenever I look at
them. They're great worn in the hair!

rows.label: qst201412_msg0011
rows.name: Don't you think that's a little childish?

rows.label: qst201412_msg0016
rows.name:
...I like what I like! There's no changing
that!

rows.label: qst201412_msg0017
rows.name: I'd say that's a win to me.

rows.label: qst201412_msg0021
rows.name:
But there's no one here to judge!
We can't decide who won with no
judge!

rows.label: qst201412_msg0023
rows.name:
It's starting to look like we might not
be able to find a winner...
